  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <head>Cēṉāvaraiyar</head>
        <p xml:lang="en">ed. <persName xml:lang="ta">Ci. Vai. Tamōtarampiḷḷai</persName> 1868, <ref target="https://archive.org/details/tolkppiyamcollat00unse/page/n85/mode/1up">82</ref>–<ref target="https://archive.org/details/tolkppiyamcollat00unse/page/n87/mode/1up">84</ref>.</p>
      <p>i - ḷ. iyaṟkai mutalāka vāḻcciyīṟākac collappaṭṭaṉavum tirintu vēṟupaṭūumaṉṉapiṟavumākiya mēṟkūṟappaṭṭa kiḻamaipporuṭkaṭ ṭōṉṟuñ collellām āṟāmvēṟṟumaittiṟattaṉaveṉṟu colluvar pulavar. e-ṟu.</p>
<p>tirintu vēṟupaṭūumaṉṉapiṟavumeṉṟārēṉum, tirintu vēṟupaṭutal aṉṉapiṟavumeṉṟataṉāṟṟaḻuvappaṭuvaṉavaṟṟuḷ orucāraṉavaṟṟiṟkē koḷka.</p>
<p>u - m. eḷḷatu kuppai; paṭaiyatu kuḻām eṉpaṉa kuḻūukkiḻamai. avai muṟaiyāṉē oṉṟu pala kuḻīiyatum vēṟu pala kuḻīiyatumām.</p>
  <lg xml:id="TolC080-Cena-cit1">
    cāttaṉatiyaṟkai;
  </lg>
  <p>nilattatakalam eṉpaṉa iyaṟkaikkiḻamai.</p>
    <lg xml:id="TolC080-Cena-cit2">
    cāttaṉatu nilaimai;
    </lg>
    <p>cāttaṉatillāmai eṉpaṉa nilaikkiḻamai. ivaiyoṉṟiyaṟkiḻamai.</p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC080-Cena-cit3">
      yāṉaiyatu kōṭu;
      </lg>
      <p>puliyatukir eṉpaṉa uṟuppiṉkiḻamai. uṟuppāvatu poruḷiṉēkatēcameṉpataṟivittaṟku oruvaḻiyuṟuppeṉṟār.</p> 
      <lg xml:id="TolC080-Cena-cit4">
      cāttaṉatu ceyaṟkai;
      </lg>
      <p>cāttaṉatu kaṟṟaṟivu eṉpaṉa ceyaṟkaikkiḻamai.</p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC080-Cena-cit5">
      aracaṉatu mutumai;
      </lg>
      <p>aracaṉatu mutirvu eṉpaṉa mutumaikkiḻamai. mutumaiyeṉpatu piṟitorkāraṇam paṟṟātu kālam paṟṟi orutalaiyāka apporuṭkaṭṭōṉṟum paruvamākaliṟ ceyaṟkaiyuḷaṭakkātu vēṟu kūṟiṉār.</p> 
      <lg xml:id="TolC080-Cena-cit6">
      cāttaṉatu toḻil;
      </lg>
      <p>cāttaṉatu celavu eṉpaṉa viṉaikkiḻamai. ivai meytirintāya taṟkiḻamai.</p>
     <lg xml:id="TolC080-Cena-cit7"> 
     cāttaṉatuṭaimai;
     </lg>
     <p>cāttaṉatu tōṭṭam eṉpaṉa uṭaimaikkiḻamai.</p> 
     <lg xml:id="TolC080-Cena-cit8">
     maṟiyatu tāy;
     </lg>
     <p>maṟiyatu tantai eṉpaṉa muṟaimaikkiḻamai.</p> 
     <lg xml:id="TolC080-Cena-cit9">
     icaiyatu karuvi;
     </lg>
     <p>vaṉaikalattatu tikiri eṉpaṉa karuvikkiḻamai.</p> 
     <lg xml:id="TolC080-Cena-cit10">
     avaṉatu tuṇai;
     </lg>
     <p>avaṉatiṇaṅku eṉpaṉa tuṇaikkiḻamai.</p>
     <lg xml:id="TolC080-Cena-cit11"> 
  nilattatoṟṟikkalam;
  </lg>
  <p>cāttaṉatu vilaittīṭṭu eṉpaṉa kalakkiḻamai.</p> 
    <lg xml:id="TolC080-Cena-cit12">
    oṟṟiyatu mutal;
    </lg>
    <p>oṟṟiyatu poruḷ eṉpaṉa mutaṟkiḻamai.</p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC080-Cena-cit13">
      kapilaratu pāṭṭu; 
      </lg>
      <p>paraṇaratu pāṭṭiyal eṉpaṉa ceyyuṭkiḻamai. terintu moḻiyāṟceyyappaṭutaliṟ ṟerintumoḻicceytiyāyiṉa. ivai poruṭpiṟitiṉkiḻamai.</p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC080-Cena-cit14">
      murukaṉatu kuṟiñcinilam;
      </lg>
      <p>veḷḷiyatāṭci eṉpaṉa kiḻamaikkiḻamai.</p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC080-Cena-cit15">
      kāṭṭatiyāṉai;
      </lg>
      <p>yāṉaiyatu kāṭu eṉpaṉa vāḻccikkiḻamai.</p> 
      <lg xml:id="TolC080-Cena-cit16">
      avaṟṟuṇ murukaṉatu kuṟiñcinilam;
      </lg>
      <p>yāṉaiyatu kāṭu eṉpaṉa nilappiṟitiṉkiḻamai. kāṭṭatiyāṉai eṉpatu poruṭpiṟitiṉkiḻamai. ēṉaiyatu kālappiṟitiṉkiḻamai.</p>
<p>tirintu vēṟupaṭūum</p>
  <lg xml:id="TolC080-Cena-cit17">
  aṉṉapiṟavum
  </lg>
  <p>eṉṟataṉāl,</p>
  <lg xml:id="TolC080-Cena-cit18">
  eṭcāntu; 
  </lg>
  <lg xml:id="TolC080-Cena-cit19">
  kōṭṭu nūṟu; 
  </lg>
  <lg xml:id="TolC080-Cena-cit20">
  cāttaṉatoppu; 
  </lg>
  <lg xml:id="TolC080-Cena-cit21">
  tokaiyatu viri; 
  </lg>
  <lg xml:id="TolC080-Cena-cit22">
  poruḷatu kēṭu; 
  </lg>
  <lg xml:id="TolC080-Cena-cit23">
  collatu poruḷ 
  </lg>
  <p>eṉṉuntoṭakkattaṉa koḷka. avaṟṟuḷ eṭcāntu; kōṭṭatu nūṟu eṉpaṉa mutalāyiṉa muḻuvatūuntiritaliṉ, vēṟu kūṟiṉār.</p>
<p>mēṟcollappaṭṭa taṟkiḻamai piṟitiṉkiḻamaiyeṉpaṉavaṟṟai virittavāṟu.	(19)</p>
    </body>
  </text>
  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <head>Nacciṉārkkiṉiyar</head>
      <p xml:lang="en">ed. <persName xml:lang="ta">Irāma. Kōvintacāmipiḷḷai</persName> 1997, <ref target="https://archive.org/details/dli.jZY9lup2kZl6TuXGlZQdjZM3kZpy.TVA_BOK_0008472/page/279/mode/1up">279</ref>–<ref target="https://archive.org/details/dli.jZY9lup2kZl6TuXGlZQdjZM3kZpy.TVA_BOK_0008472/page/280/mode/1up">280</ref>.</p>
      <p>iḵtu, ataṉai muṭikka varum poruḷ vēṟupāṭu kūṟukiṉṟatu.

(i-ḷ.)iyaṟkai......vāḻcciyiṉ- iyaṟkkai mutalāka vāḻcci īṟākac collappaṭṭaṉavum,tirintu vēṟu paṭūum aṉṉa piṟavum- oru cāraṉa tirintu vēṟupaṭum avai pōlavaṉa piṟavumākiya, kūṟiya maruṅkil tōṉṟum kiḷavi- muṟkūṟiya kiḻamaip poruṭkaṇ tōṉṟum col ellām, ānaṉ pāla eṉmaṉār pulavar- āṟām vēṟṟumait tiṟattaṉa eṉṟu kūṟuvar pulavar(e-ṟu.)

(u-m.)1eṇṇatu kuppai- iḵtu, oṉṟupala kuḻīiya taṟkiḻamai.

2.paṭaiyatu kuḻām_itu, vēṟu pala kuḻīiya taṟkiḻamai.

3.cāttaṉatu iyaṟkai,

nilattu akalam_ivai, iyaṟkaikkiḻamai.

4.cāttaṉatu nilaimai,

cāttaṉatu illāmai_ivai, nilaikkiḻamai.

innāṉkum oṉṟiyaṟkiḻamai.

oru poruḷiṉ ēkatēcam aṟivittaṟku `oruvaḻi uṟuppu' eṉṟār. avai,

yāṉaiyatu kōṭu,

puliyatu ukir_ivai, uṟuppiṉ kiḻamai.

ceyaṟkaiyāvatu, taṉ taṉmai tirintu vēṟōr taṉmai ātal. avai,

cāttaṉatu ceyaṟkai,

cāttaṉatu kaṟṟaṟivu.

mutumaik kiḻamai,

aracaṉatu mutumai,

aracaṉatu mutirvu.

iḵtu aṟiviṉ mutircci eṉpatu aṟivittaṟku iḷamai kūṟāyiṉār.

viṉaik kiḻamai,

cāttaṉatu viṉai,

cāttaṉatu celavu.

ivai, mey tirintu āya taṟkiḻamai.

uṭaimaik kiḻamai,

cāttaṉatu uṭaimai,

cāttaṉatu tōṭṭam.

muṟaimaik kiḻamai,

maṟiyatu tāy,

maṟiyatu tantai.

karuvik kiḻamai,

icaiyatu karuvi,

viṉaik kālattatu tikiri.

tuṇaikkiḻamai,

avaṉatu tuṇai,

avaṉatu iṇaṅku.

kālamāvatu, ōlai.

nilattatu oṟṟikkalam,

cāttaṉatu vilait tīṭṭu.

iḵtu, iru poruṭku urimai uṭaimaiyiṉ, uṭaimaiyiṉ vēṟāyiṟṟu.

mutaṟkiḻamai,

oṟṟiyatu mutal,

oṟṟiyatu poruḷ.

terintu moḻic ceyti, terintu moḻiyāl ceyyappaṭutaliṉ terintu moḻic ceyti āyiṟṟu.

kapilaratu pāṭṭu

itu `pāriyatu pāṭṭu' eṉavum niṟṟaliṉ, iruporuṭku uriyatām.

paraṇaratu pāṭṭiyal

ituvum atu. ivai poruṭpiṟitiṉ kiḻamai.

kiḻamaik kiḻamai,

murukaṉatu kuṟiñci nilam.

itu nilappiṟitiṉ kiḻamai.

veḷḷiyatu āṭci

itu kālappiṟitiṉ kiḻamai.

vāḻcci,

kāṭṭatu yāṉai.

itu poruṭpiṟitiṉ kiḻamai.

yāṉaiyatu kāṭu.

itu nilappiṟitiṉ kiḻamai.

vāḻcci, vāḻtalai uṇarttuṅkāl taṟkiḻamaiyumām.

`aṉṉa piṟavum' eṉṟatu,

eṭcāntu,

kōṭṭu nūṟu.

ivai muḻutun tirintaṉa.

cāttaṉatu oppu,

tokaiyatu viri,

poruḷatu kēṭu,

collatu poruḷ.

ivai ciṟitu tirintaṉa.</p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC250-Nacc-cit1">
      </lg>
    </body>
